Package org.codehaus.cargo.container.configuration

Class ConfigurationType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codehaus.cargo.container.configuration.ConfigurationType
  • public class ConfigurationType
extends Object
    Configuration type of Configurations. There are currently 3 types: Standalone local, Existing local and runtime configurations.
